I don't think it ever got past the beta stage and you can only use it in Blitz 
mode to AGA screenmodes.

I'd recommend not using it, Mildred (http://www.stationone.demon.co.uk) is far 
better.

However, if you really really want it, it will be on BUMs 9 and 10, also in the 
BUM 9 and 10 drawers on the Ultimate BB CD. You may also be able to find a link 
to it from http://www.blitz-
2000.freeserve.co.uk/archives/libraries/libraries.html but that page was 
donated by another site, so if it was stored local to that site, you might not 
be able to get it. (And it might not be on that page).


