Subject: Do...Loops
X-UIDL: 7d4d9607c145d0318e88f8c9eca9dc4f

Hi,
   Is it possible to do a loop, with If...Then statements, without
hogging the CPU? Like this:

Repeat
  x=Rnd(500)
  If x=>100
    ...
    ...
  EndIf
  If x<=400
    ...
    ...
  EndIf
Forever

And still have the CPU usage at a low, like when using WaitEvent? 
Cya!
Gaz.
