@NODE "Mail_177" "Flickering display"
From: Stephen Lebed <slebed@earthlink.net>
Date: Sun, 06 Jun 1999 22:13:39 -0800
Subject: Flickering display
X-UIDL: 6cfa3c60d341c7032d9f931b691a3263

Hi all,

I have a strange problem.  I've opened a cybergraphx screen 640x480
256colors.  I have a code loop that is something like this...

Repeat
    blah
    blah
    Change color values using AGAPalRGB 0,nn,rr,gg,bb
    Show Palette 0
Until Trigger is pressed

The Show Palette command causes the display to have sporatic pixel
flickering.

Use Palette also causes this problem.  If I add WaitTOF_ or Vwait, the
problem persists.

Any ideas on how a can fix this?
-- 
Thanks in advance,

Stephen Lebed
slebed@earthlink.net


