@NODE "Mail_223" "Re: Grand Theft AMiGA (Oh no, not again!)"
From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Wed, 09 Jun 1999 06:11:52 -0500
Subject: Re: Grand Theft AMiGA (Oh no, not again!)
