function to draw borders on the menu screens. To delete them, I simply
put down identical text/box using colour 0 (I'm using a black
background). The problem is that the graphics are not completly drawn
over. Sometimes the text stays on screen, and parts (but not all) of
the boxes are left behind. I've tried putting a VWait after the
commands to get rid of the boxes, and the program structure is too
simple for it to be 'skipping' the section of code that handles
