@NODE "Mail_321" "Re: I`m gonna take up C again"
From: "David McMinn" <D.Mcminn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Wed, 23 Jun 1999 10:39:22 +0100
Subject: Re: I`m gonna take up C again
