Hi Anders

> I can't see that you have allocated memory for the structure
> mylib is supposed to point to. You just write somewhere
> random in memory.

You don't need to allocate memory for use with OpenLibrary, as it returns a 
pointer to the library. The OS takes care of allocating memory (if it is not 
already in memory).


