After messing about with the v37 stuff, I just thought I`d mention that the
newvoice structure in Blitz sets all the new variables up as BYTEs - not a
problem, unless you`re using slider gadgets to set the values, as some go
from 0-255, and since Blitz doesn`t provide a UBYTE, you have to be careful
with WORDS and BYTES.

VIC




