@NODE "Mail_514" "Re: Point and Plot."
Sender: tdc98@doc.ic.ac.uk
Date: Sun, 20 Jun 1999 20:03:29 +0100
From: Thomas Cobb <tdc98@doc.ic.ac.uk>
Subject: Re: Point and Plot.
Encoding: 7bit
