Rob Hutchinson wrote:

> That is why it takes so long.
>
> What was the point in this then? To reduce memory that the Bitmap takes
> up?

No, the bitmap is still taking up the same amount of space.  I think the reason is that in this
form the data is easier to manipulate if you want to do scrolling.  Compare scrolling 2D games on
the Amiga to those on the PC and you'll notice the difference.

    Thom


