	Yes, exactly in the same way (functionname followed with an underscore
ie: Wait_()). But for all libraries which need to be opened (all execpt
dos, gfx, exec and intuition) there will be a special function to
open it and know if the library is really found or not. Blitz
doesn't allow that and that was shade.

