> How do you make a progress bar with gadtools or something(not mui)? I dont
> think I`ve read anything about that in the docs.

If I were doing one, I`d simply print blue spaces, using the WJam modes, in
a bevel box.  I was considering this - but considered that during file
access, it wouldn cause problems, as you would need to keep changing the
output to the window, and then back to the file - just a thought.

VIC



