I've tried Event=$8 but tha tonly works witha  window presnet

I've tried WaitEvent but that halts flow, stopping the text from
appearing, and I've tried searching for a command similar to AM*S's
MouseKey command.

Any ideas?

PLEASE help me!

Also, would any1 like to beta-test the finished game? It's gonna be
totally written in Blitz (hopeefully) as I'm trying to draw myself
away from my fixation with AM*S. :-)

