Oh,no, You misunderstand..... 
The point of the Stack changing code isn`t for the editor, it`s for the
final EXE,.. You see as MCC`s need a lot of stack, the code would append
the amount needed by all your MCC`s/MUI to the AStack variable and
then your program is gaurenteed to run from CLI as well as from an
icon!!... See? 

