X-UIDL: 04e31cf991fb641e4529fa41b6fd6a46

> I'm trying to test out UPD using the UPD Chat V2.5 with the Blitz
> extension, but it won't compile.  I followed the directions for installing
> UPD, adding TCPtoBlitz extension, ect, ect.  When I try to compile it, I
> get a 'Type Not Found'  error.  It stops on the line
> 
> *scr.Screen=Peek.l(Addr Screen(0))
> 
> I have Amigalibs.res in the compiler options, but do I need anything else?

You probably have version 2 of the amigalibs.res file, in which case you should 
do:

*scr._Screen=Peek.l(Addr Screen(0))


