Subject: Re: Waitevent and loops
Encoding: 8bit
X-UIDL: 494e0c4b85c3e4be0d1cfde688d690dd

Hello Oliver

On 06-Jun-99, Oliver Marks set out across the seas with this message:

OM> The only way i can get around this is to write the text scroller as a
OM> seperate program and then load it up on to the current screen.
OM> Anyone know of a better way to get around this problem?

Yes.  Use ev.l=#Event# instead of ev.l=#WaitEvent#.

Regards
