Encoding: 8bit
X-UIDL: e169176102f72d72c0975b62a7cb98a0

On 6 Jun 99 Toby Zuijdveld wrote about 'Waitevent and loops'.

 TZ> Yes.  Use ev.l=#Event# instead of ev.l=#WaitEvent#.

If you are going to do this, put a Delay_(5) in the main loop, otherwise
your code will be busy looping and running at 100% CPU.

Simon Archer


