my Blitz BASIC beat-em-up Legend of the Exploding Fist. They are the XB 
(or CrossBones) Sound Library and the LE Shapes Library which contains 
improved shape storage and access commands. Does anyone know where I can 
find these rare beasts...?

Kind regards,
Ian Paul Andrews.

